item.title: Week 3: What's Happening? Where have I been?
item.description: “How did it get so late so soon?” ― Dr. Seuss Welcome everyone, this is your host Nikhil Maan aka Sc0rpi0n101 and we’re running late on everything this week. This time we will talk about some operating system stuff along with the week’s work. I will have more blogs on operating systems and that type of stuff soon. For now, let’s talk about what’s happening. Why so Late?
